	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum te rogo amanter, <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingere</persName> clarissime, ut ad me, si quid in comitiis praesentibus acciderit, quod nostra interfuturum existimaris, scribere et tuo pro candore agere, ut soles, velis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nil te caelabunt legati neque recondita peto senatus nostri nomine, sed ea tantum, quae vel convivis vel congerronibus tuto exponi queant.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid accesserit reliquit, hoc plus tibi omnes gratiae debebimus et referemus; nihil autem dubita, quin omnia sancta fide sint intra parietes (ut vulgo dicitur) senatorios mansura.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> nihildum novi, nisi quod caesar altis consiliis inhiat.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dies dictus est duci <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572" cert="high">Wirttenbergensi</placeName> a <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinando</persName> actore et ordinati iudices, qui de possessione ducatus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtenbergensis</placeName> cognoscant et pronuncient.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Er hat die sach vor außwurf an?</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">verloren.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectant boni omnes, quam diu dominus horum hominum fastum plus quam immodicum sit laturus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De colloquio eruditorum ne iota quidem ad me scribitur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6355" cert="high">Saylerus</persName> schedulam misit, in quo notantur quidam nescio puri an impuri, qui sint a statibus suffragante caesare delecti, ut de medio aliquo mitigandae controversiae in caussa religionis deliberent et consultent, quam ego ad te mitto cum scheda pridie mihi a <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p506" cert="high">Buttlero</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglo</placeName>, cive <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l257" cert="high">Constantiensi</placeName>, donata.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiebat, eam ex <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4863">Fuggarorum</persName> aedibus missam multa cum fide; at ego nugas Martias esse arbitror.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magis placuerunt epigrammata et epitaphia, quae propinquus meus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6355" cert="high">Saylerus</persName> misit, quae et ipsa mitto, longe optime vir, ne quid te caelem nugarum domesticarum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale et collegium meo nomine salvum iube.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l473" cert="high">Sangalli</placeName>, XII. die Martii, anno domini MDXLVIII.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadianus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, clarissimae urbis <placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> episcopo, domino et amico inprimis colendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
